## ⚠️ КРИТИЧНО: Инфраструктура для MMOFPS

**ОБЯЗАТЕЛЬНЫЕ настройки для production game servers:**

### 1. Kubernetes Resources (правильные лимиты)

```yaml
# Issue: #123
# Game server pod с правильными ресурсами
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: game-server
spec:
  containers:
  - name: game-server
    resources:
      requests:
        memory: "512Mi"    # Минимум для старта
        cpu: "500m"        # 0.5 CPU
      limits:
        memory: "2Gi"      # Max для game server
        cpu: "2000m"       # 2 CPU max
    
    # CPU pinning для game servers (latency critical)
    securityContext:
      capabilities:
        add: ["SYS_NICE"] # Для real-time priority
```

**Результат:** Stable performance, no throttling

### 2. Horizontal Pod Autoscaler (для API services)

```yaml
# Issue: #123
# Auto-scale при нагрузке
apiVersion: autoscaling/v2
kind: HorizontalPodAutoscaler
metadata:
  name: matchmaking-service-hpa
spec:
  scaleTargetRef:
    apiVersion: apps/v1
    kind: Deployment
    name: matchmaking-service
  minReplicas: 3
  maxReplicas: 20
  metrics:
  - type: Resource
    resource:
      name: cpu
      target:
        type: Utilization
        averageUtilization: 70  # Scale at 70% CPU
  - type: Resource
    resource:
      name: memory
      target:
        type: Utilization
        averageUtilization: 80
  behavior:
    scaleUp:
      stabilizationWindowSeconds: 60
      policies:
      - type: Percent
        value: 50  # Scale up 50% at a time
        periodSeconds: 60
```

### 3. Pod Disruption Budget (для availability)

```yaml
# Issue: #123
# Защита critical services от одновременного shutdown
apiVersion: policy/v1
kind: PodDisruptionBudget
metadata:
  name: game-server-pdb
spec:
  minAvailable: 80%  # Минимум 80% pods должны быть доступны
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: game-server
```

### 4. Network Policies (изоляция для security)

```yaml
# Issue: #123
# Game servers принимают только UDP на game port
apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: NetworkPolicy
metadata:
  name: game-server-netpol
spec:
  podSelector:
    matchLabels:
      app: game-server
  policyTypes:
  - Ingress
  - Egress
  ingress:
  - from:
    - podSelector: {} # Any pod
    ports:
    - protocol: UDP
      port: 7777  # Game port
  egress:
  - to:
    - podSelector:
        matchLabels:
          app: database
    ports:
    - protocol: TCP
      port: 5432
```

### 5. Prometheus Metrics (мониторинг)

```yaml
# Issue: #123
# ServiceMonitor для автоматического scraping
apiVersion: monitoring.coreos.com/v1
kind: ServiceMonitor
metadata:
  name: game-server-metrics
spec:
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: game-server
  endpoints:
  - port: metrics
    interval: 15s  # Scrape каждые 15 секунд
    path: /metrics
```

**Обязательные метрики для game servers:**
- `game_server_player_count` - текущие игроки
- `game_server_tick_duration_seconds` - время game tick
- `game_server_network_bytes_sent/received` - сетевой трафик
- `game_server_match_duration_seconds` - длительность матчей

### 6. Loki для логирования (structured logs)

```yaml
# Issue: #123
# Promtail config для сбора логов
apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: promtail-config
data:
  promtail.yaml: |
    server:
      http_listen_port: 9080
    
    clients:
    - url: http://loki:3100/loki/api/v1/push
    
    scrape_configs:
    - job_name: kubernetes-pods
      kubernetes_sd_configs:
      - role: pod
      relabel_configs:
      - source_labels: [__meta_kubernetes_pod_label_app]
        target_label: app
      - source_labels: [__meta_kubernetes_namespace]
        target_label: namespace
```

### 7. Grafana Dashboards (для дебага)

**Обязательные дашборды:**
- **Game Server Overview:** Player count, TPS, latency, memory
- **Network Performance:** Bandwidth, packet loss, RTT
- **Database Performance:** Query time, connections, slow queries
- **Application Metrics:** Request rate, error rate, duration

### 8. Alerting Rules (критичные алерты)

```yaml
# Issue: #123
# Prometheus alerts для game servers
apiVersion: monitoring.coreos.com/v1
kind: PrometheusRule
metadata:
  name: game-server-alerts
spec:
  groups:
  - name: game-server
    interval: 30s
    rules:
    - alert: HighGameServerLatency
      expr: histogram_quantile(0.99, game_server_tick_duration_seconds) > 0.05
      for: 5m
      labels:
        severity: warning
      annotations:
        summary: "Game server P99 latency > 50ms"
    
    - alert: GameServerDown
      expr: up{job="game-server"} == 0
      for: 1m
      labels:
        severity: critical
      annotations:
        summary: "Game server is down"
    
    - alert: HighMemoryUsage
      expr: container_memory_usage_bytes / container_spec_memory_limit_bytes > 0.9
      for: 5m
      labels:
        severity: warning
      annotations:
        summary: "Container memory usage > 90%"
```

### 9. Readiness/Liveness Probes (правильная конфигурация)

```yaml
# Issue: #123
# Проверки здоровья сервиса
spec:
  containers:
  - name: game-server
    livenessProbe:
      httpGet:
        path: /health
        port: 8080
      initialDelaySeconds: 30
      periodSeconds: 10
      timeoutSeconds: 5
      failureThreshold: 3
    
    readinessProbe:
      httpGet:
        path: /ready
        port: 8080
      initialDelaySeconds: 10
      periodSeconds: 5
      timeoutSeconds: 3
      successThreshold: 1
      failureThreshold: 3
    
    # Startup probe для медленного старта
    startupProbe:
      httpGet:
        path: /health
        port: 8080
      failureThreshold: 30
      periodSeconds: 10
```

### 10. Affinity Rules (для optimal placement)

```yaml
# Issue: #123
# Размести game servers на разных нодах для HA
spec:
  affinity:
    podAntiAffinity:
      preferredDuringSchedulingIgnoredDuringExecution:
      - weight: 100
        podAffinityTerm:
          labelSelector:
            matchLabels:
              app: game-server
          topologyKey: kubernetes.io/hostname
    
    # Game servers на выделенных нодах
    nodeAffinity:
      requiredDuringSchedulingIgnoredDuringExecution:
        nodeSelectorTerms:
        - matchExpressions:
          - key: node-type
            operator: In
            values:
            - game-server  # Выделенные ноды для game
```

**ВАЖНО:** Game servers требуют особой инфраструктуры - low latency, high CPU, UDP support. Эти конфигурации обеспечивают production-ready deployment.

## ⚠️ ВАЖНО: Оптимизация Docker и Kubernetes

Все сервисы унифицированы: Dockerfile используют Go 1.24, multi-stage builds, security contexts (non-root user), health checks. Kubernetes deployments включают security contexts, startup/liveness/readiness probes, HPA/PDB для критичных сервисов. Используй существующие паттерны из других сервисов.

